Pre-Game Insights: Nepal return to the T20 World Cup after 10 years
Nepal's captain Rohit Paudel is confident that his side will start the T20 World Cup with a win against Netherlands
Netherlands' coach Ryan Cook said his team will be wary of the threat Nepal pose
Head to head: Nepal and Netherlands have won five and six of their 11 T20Is, respectively
Form: Both sides head into the match with a mixed run of form
